=== Etymology ===
From {{L.}} [[cursus]], past participle of [[correre]] ''to run''

===Pronunciation===
*kôrs, /kɔː(r)s/, /kO:(r)s/
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔː(r)s|-ɔː(r)s]]

====Homophones====
